  "description": "<p>Brighter and more user-friendly than ever before, Petzl\u2019s Actik is here to light up your adventures. The narrow and wide beams can be used on their own or together, great for running in low light. Up to 450 lumens and reflective details on the strap to help you see and be seen.</p><ul><li>5 modes, 3 in white light: high (2h at 450 lumens), medium (10h at 100 lumens), low (100h at 7 lumens), 2 in red: continuous  (60h at 2 lumens) and strobe (400h at 2 lumens). Runtimes from use with 3 AAA batteries, CORE battery runtimes will differ</li><li>Wide and narrow beams provide the right light for nearly any activity</li><li>Red LED is great for preserving night vision and not disturbing tent mates</li><li>Compatible with CORE rechargeable battery pack and Ni-MH rechargeable batteries (neither included)</li><li>IPX4 water proofing keeps the light keeps shining even when Mother Nature has other ideas</li><li>Centre-mounted pivot lets you aim the light up or down</li><li>Glow in the dark reflector ring helps you find your light in the dark</li><li>Reflective detailing on the headband helps keep you seen</li><li>Updated strap uses a dual sliding buckle system that is faster and easier to adjust than previous generations</li><li>Lockout mode prevents light from being switched on inside your pack</li><li>Included white storage pouch doubles as a light diffusing lantern</li></ul>",
